{"tid":134863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"賊媒100毛終極打手廣告狂人：抄少咗或無咁明顯就無問題啦","createTime":"2017-02-25T20:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T20:21:09.000Z","uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"492875910391bc2d1517a402ee0a588474c2e826","tid":134863,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0H9Hh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0H9Hh5.jpg&h=9b75a379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/26/040556_cfdaaa77e6ebcc96a9d6059173de0daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F26%2F040556_cfdaaa77e6ebcc96a9d6059173de0daf.jpg&h=36eba23d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y709y4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy709y4r.jpg&h=bb77f956&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/26/041343_3697015b4fb728a4086ec894a9efc840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F26%2F041343_3697015b4fb728a4086ec894a9efc840.jpg&h=1ada5e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛粉話班媒紙葡萄，但人地係不屑做出D仆街嘢<br />\n個廣告狂人最賤格係扮中立，係篇嘢又話唔會為100毛捍衛，但回覆就撐到上天，借意搵班毛粉嚟網絡批鬥<br />\n<br />\n睇到廣告狂人個post D100毛打手真係想笑出聲<br />\n同埋可以正式宣布廣告狂人係100毛頭號打手<br />\n盲撐到失去人格可以講得出偷嘢偷少左或偷完無俾人發覺就無問題"},{"pid":"77447ffdeff024201a0ad1551a927beb4fc99612","tid":134863,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:16:24.000Z","msg":"另一個post<br />\n《晚吹》成班做紙媒嘅一齊屌100毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/132334/page/10?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/132334/page/10?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7cdfecdd5dea53ee59275f3b8f6774b321494212","tid":134863,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:16:36.000Z","msg"